<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\nouicompat\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}{\f1\fswiss\fprq2 Aptos;}{\f2\fswiss\fprq2\fcharset0 Aptos;}}
{\*\generator Riched20 10.0.19041}\viewkind4\uc1 
\pard\b\f0\fs20 28/10/2024: \par

\pard\widctlpar\b0 Table initialization: \line\f1\fs20 TCACHEBANTECL;TCACHESEGMENTATION: TCACHESEGMT;TCACHESEGTYPE;TSTAMP\f2\fs22\par

\pard\b\f0\fs20\par
2024-10-16: Retro T&amp;S Initiatives, Non Proportionnal Retrocession Plan\par
\b0 2 new columns are added in TSEGTYPE\par
- the Retro Underwriting Year - RTY_NF\par
- the Segmentation Mode - SGTTYPMOD_NT\par
\par
\par
2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Creation of whole domain\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Added Simulation Environment table\par
- SCOR comments on previous version taken into account\par
- Clarified storage location (InfoMega vs TP)\par
\par
2013-06-25 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- table TSEGMENTATION: Change type of SSD_CF to SSD_CF instead of char(3)\par
\par
2013-07-10 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Remove simulation environments\par
\par
2013-09-04 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Add END_NT  and PLC_NT in TSEGRUNERR and TSEGRUNERR_H &amp; _S\par
- Add TSEGBATCHPLAN table\par
- Remove TSEGUWASMSEC_S and TSEGUWRETPLC_S tables (simulation)\par
- Remove columns: ROWID_NT, CLUSTER_NT, timestamp, CRE_D, LSTUPD_D columns from TSEGUWASMSEC and TSEGUWRETPLC\par
- Add column SGTSCOPE_CT in TSEGRUN table\par
- Add column SGTUWLEN_NB and SGTUWORDER_NB in TSEGUWCOLUMN table\par
\par
2013-09-05 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
useless mandatory field UWY in TSEGEXCEPT\par
\par
2013-09-10 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
SGMT_CF datatype changed from &#39;char(8)&#39; to to &#39;int&#39;\par
\par
2013-09-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- SGMT_CF changed to SGMT_NF\par
\par
2013-09-24 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- datatype SGTCRI_CF in TSEGMENTRULE2CRI changed from int to L16\par
\par
2013-09-24 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
CRE_D and CREUSR_CF removed from TSEGRUNRES* and TSEGRUNERR* tables\par
\par
2013-10-07 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- set column TSEGBATCHPLAN..LASTSGTRUN_NT nullable\par
\par
2013-10-07 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- TSEGUWRETPLC table : Rename columns RTY_NF to UWY_Nf and RETCTR_NF to CTR_NF\par
\par
2013-11-06 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Duplidate tables TSEGUWASMSEC and TSEGUWRETPLC for every production site (FRA1, SGP1, USA1) and move them in the BTRAVI schema.\par
- Add the section in the pk of TSEGUWRETPLC tables\par
\par
2013-11-08 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Criteria column length from L16 to L32 in TSEGCRITERIA\par
\par
2013-11-20 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Adding table TUWEXPORT\par
\par
2013-11-26 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- set PRDSIT_CF nullable of table TSEGRUN\par
- add SSD_CF column on TSEGRUNRES, TSEGRUNRES_H, TSEGRUNRES_S, TSEGRUNERR, TSEGRUNERR_H, TSEGRUNERR_S\par
}
