<a:Modifier>frxb406</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This Diagram presents all the tables specific to the Omega 2.0 Segmentation domain, as well as their relationships.
It is structured in two ways :
- contract portfolio (source data to the segmentation) vs segmentation
- administration vs operation (actual results of the configuration)
</a:Comment>
