\pard\b\f0\fs20 2024-10-16: Retro T&amp;S Initiatives, Non Proportionnal Retrocession Plan\b0\par
2 new columns are added in TSEGTYPE\par
- the Retro Underwriting Year - RTY_NF\par
- the Segmentation Mode - SGTTYPMOD_NT\par
\par
\par
2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Creation\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Added the TSEFRUNSIMUENV table in the Segmentation Operation area.\par
- Precised the set of pure &quot;InfoMega&quot; tables (i.e. not present in the TP database)\par
}
</a:Description>
