<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1392816992</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table defines the different Segments of a given Segmentation.
In case of Level 0 Segment, its portfolio selection criteria are managed via sub-Rules.
For other levels, they simply aggregate other Segments of lower level.</a:Comment>
