<a:Comment>ID of the Parent Segment. This ID is set and mandatory if the Segment is not of the max. Level defined for the Segmentation (see TSEGMENTLVL table). It is not set if the Segment is of max. Level. It should reference a Segment (of the same Segmentation) one level higher.   a Segme</a:Comment>
