<o:Table Id="o92">
<a:ObjectID>9DC3EB83-BC96-44EB-8F88-EDBE5B2C730E</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation Result</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGRUNRES</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1366028729</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1393340655</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table contains the results of the evaluation of one single Segmentation.
It contains results of a run in production mode, history mode or simulation mode.

Threse is exactly one table created for one run, therefore there are mutliple instances of this table.
Each instance has a different name (composed with the run identifier).
This table can be partitioned on segment number (SGMT_NF).</a:Comment>
<a:Generated>0</a:Generated>
<a:PhysicalOptions>on SGMT_NF</a:PhysicalOptions>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
