<o:Table Id="o95">
<a:ObjectID>5ACE7026-9602-4DE0-B182-FA8794B621A8</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation Run</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGRUN</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1366031267</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1393844167</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table tracks the different segmentation executions done.
A new entry is created each time the segmentation engine starts to process a given Segmentation version (current active in production, draft one for simulation) on a Segmentation portfolio.
Results of this segmentation are stored in differentTSEGRUNRES tables according to the Segmentation evaluation type (production or simulation) and if a Snapshot is required.
Segmentation errors are stored in matching TSEGRUNERR tables.</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Creation\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- last update fields become mandatory\par
- Added link to simulation Environment\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
-Update banalised codifications\par
\par
2013-10-07 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Remove simulation environments \par
\par
2013-09-04 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Add SGTSCOPE_CT column\par
\par
2013-11-26 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- set PRDSIT_CF nullable\par
}
</a:Description>
