<o:Table Id="o100">
<a:ObjectID>7769D66C-BAD5-49D9-A557-BED49A500337</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation Error</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGRUNERR</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1366288778</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1393339769</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table contains the Errors raised during the evaluation of one single Segmentation
It contains errors of a  run in production mode, history mode or simulation mode.
This happens among mainly if a portfolio element matches several Segments inside a Segmentation with no priorities.

Threse is exactly one table created for one run, therefore there are mutliple instances of this table.
Each instance has a different name (composed with the run identifier).
</a:Comment>
<a:Generated>0</a:Generated>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
