\par
2013-10-07 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Rename columns RTY_NF to UWY_Nf and RETCTR_NF to CTR_NF\par
\par
2013-11-06 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Duplicate for production site FRA1\par
- Add Section in the PK\par
}
