<o:Table Id="o114">
<a:ObjectID>DDBAD610-28E0-41D7-AB2A-3A3225E17337</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Link between criteria and segmentation rule</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGMENTRULE2CRI</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1368538228</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1380905854</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table tracks all Portfolio Criteria used in Segment Rules.
These elements enable to identify Portfolio Criteria actually used in production.
Rules may use only Portfolio Criteria of scope and granularity matching their Segmentations (respectively SGTSCOPE_CT fields in TSEGTYPE and TSEGCATSCOPE tables and SGTGRAN_CT fields in TSEGMENTATION and TSEGCATGRAN tables) .
Entries are automatically added/removed upon modification of each Rule definition.</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
