<o:Table Id="o115">
<a:ObjectID>3210685A-3068-430D-A92A-AC82A18210C2</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Segmentation&#39;s Included Contract Statuses</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEG2CTRSTS</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1369298997</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>u000289</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1380904348</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXB156</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table defines the scope of Contract Statuses on which a Segmentation is applied.
It is filled only in case of custom Contract Status scope (see ALLCTRSTS_B field of the TSEGMENTATION table).
Otherwise, all default stasuses are considered.</a:Comment>
