<o:Table Id="o129">
<a:ObjectID>213BFBCD-8219-4413-81FD-E5388AAFFC80</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Assumed Contract Section Segmentation Portfolio3</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGUWASMSEC_USA1</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1383733312</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1383733683</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXA567</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table contains the current Segmentation Portfolio of Assumed Contract Sections for production site USA1
It should match an entry of the TSEGUWTABLE Segmentation portfolio table.
The current model describes the core fields of the table, this table being dynamically extended according to the Criteria columns defined for this portfolio table in the TSEGUWCOLUMN table.
This table is populated on a daily basis by extracting assumed Contract Sections&#39; data from various sources (mainly BFAC &amp; BTRT databases).
It is also dynamically extended with one column per &quot;active&quot; Segment Type containing a denormalised version of the Segmentation results (TSEGRUNRES).</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
<a:Description>{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg1252\deff0\deflang1036{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset0 Times New Roman;}}
{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.21.2510;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\f0\fs20 2013-05-29 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Creation\par
\par
2013-06-17 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- last update fields become mandatory\par
\par
2013-06-25 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Adding BANTEC codification for CTRSTS_CT\par
\par
2013-09-04 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Remove columns ROWID_NT, CLUSTER_NT, timestamp, CRE_D, LSTUPD_D\par
\par
2013-11-06 / Omega 2-Phase 1B&#39;-OM-B-TRA01\par
- Duplicate for production site USA1\par
}
</a:Description>
