<o:Table Id="o131">
<a:ObjectID>F5EDAABB-B4E5-4F5B-BB95-966D2AF71B69</a:ObjectID>
<a:Name>Retrocession Contract Placement Segmentation Portfolio2</a:Name>
<a:Code>TSEGUWRETPLC_SGP1</a:Code>
<a:CreationDate>1383733335</a:CreationDate>
<a:Creator>FRXA567</a:Creator>
<a:ModificationDate>1383744302</a:ModificationDate>
<a:Modifier>FRXA567</a:Modifier>
<a:Comment>This table contains the current Segmentation Portfolio of Retrocession Contract Placements for production site SGP1
It should match an entry of the TSEGUWTABLE Segmentation portfolio table.
The current model describes the core fields of the table, this table being dynamically extended according to the Criteria columns defined for this portfolio table in the TSEGUWCOLUMN table.
This table is populated on a daily basis by extracting retrocession Contract Placements&#39; data from various sources (mainly BRET database). 
It is also dynamically extended with one column per &quot;active&quot; Segment Type containing a denormalised version of the Segmentation results (TSEGRUNRES).</a:Comment>
<a:TotalSavingCurrency/>
